title: How to Adult?! | Staytion Lifestyle Centre @ Dhoby Ghaut MRT (Dhoby Xchange), Singapore, SG | July 18, 2024
text: How to Adult?! Schedule Thu Jul 18 2024 at 07:30 pm to 10:00 pmUTC+08:00 Location Staytion Lifestyle Centre @ Dhoby Ghaut MRT (Dhoby Xchange) | Singapore, SG About this Event If you're wondering the same, this suits you! "How to Adult?!" a get connected community series designed specifically for young adults aged 18 to 35. This event is a unique opportunity to connect with peers and aspiring mentors in a supportive and engaging environment. Whether you're looking to make new friends, finding mentors, or exploring new hobbies, new insights or career paths, this series has something for everyone. (Dinner will be provided) Purpose: The goal of "How to Adult" is to create a space where young adults can build meaningful connections. Through a variety of activities and discussions, participants will have the chance to meet others with similar interests and aspirations. The event is designed to help you: - Expand your social circle and make new friends - Connect with mentor 1-1 who can provide guidance and support - Discover and pursue new hobbies Join Us: Don't miss out on this opportunity to connect with like-minded individuals and enhance your personal and professional growth. Join us today for an enriching experience that will help you navigate the journey of adulthood with confidence and support.
